	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-172808767" class="story-title"> <a   href="//news.slashdot.org/story/24/01/24/048249/alaska-air-ceo-says-loose-bolts-found-in-many-boeing-jets">Alaska Air CEO Says Loose Bolts Found in 'Many' Boeing Jets</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/alaska-air-ceo-says-loose-bolts-found-in-many-boeing-max-jets"  title="External link - https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/alaska-air-ceo-says-loose-bolts-found-in-many-boeing-max-jets" target="_blank"> (bloomberg.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
		<!--<span class="comments commentcnt-172808767" >175</span>-->
		

		
		<!-- comment bubble -->
		
			<span class="comment-bubble"><a href="//news.slashdot.org/story/24/01/24/048249/alaska-air-ceo-says-loose-bolts-found-in-many-boeing-jets#comments" title="">175</a></span>
		
	</h2>
	<div class="details" id="details-172808767">
		<span class="story-details">
		<span class="story-views">
